@startuml Workflow Two Sequence Diagram
title Workflow 2: Display Playlist Stats

actor User
participant "DatabaseGUI (Presentation Layer)" as GUI
participant "PlaylistController (BLL)" as PC
participant "PlaylistDataProvider (DAL)" as DP
database "Database" as DB

User -> GUI : Select "Get Playlist Stats"
User -> GUI : Enter UserId + PlaylistName
User -> GUI : Click Load

GUI -> PC : playlistStats(userId, playlistName)
PC -> DP : getPlaylistStats(userId, playlistName)

DP -> DB : CALL GetPlaylistStats(userId, playlistName)
DB --> DP : ResultSet (SongName, Plays, Skips, LastPlayed)

DP -> DP : Convert ResultSet → List<PlaylistStat>
DP --> PC : List<PlaylistStat>

PC --> GUI : List<PlaylistStat>

GUI -> GUI : showStatsTable(list)
GUI -> GUI : Render JTable (Song, Plays, Skips, LastPlayed)
GUI -> User: Display Stats Table

@enduml